                     <interp inst="t18200412-67-person632" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am a warehouseman, and live near the prosecutor. I saw the prisoner about half-past four o'clock in the afternoon, take a piece of ribbon out of the window, and put it into his pocket. A pane of glass was broken - I secured him. Another boy was with him whom I suspected.</p>
               <p>(Property produced and sworn to.)</p>
